-- Mauritius Exports Fell 4% in First 2 Months, Le Mauricien Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-03-16T13:31:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-16/mauritius-exports-fell-4-in-first-2-months-le-mauricien-says.html
Mauritius exports declined 4
percent in the first two months of the year from a year earlier,
led by slower demand from the U.K. and  France , Port Louis-based
Le Mauricien reported, citing Industry Minister Cader Sayed-
Hossen.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
